== PHPUnit for [[http://www.pimcore.org|Pimcore]] ==

=== About Pimunit===

[x] Easy to use

[x] Write tests for Pimcore, Website and Plugins

[x] Use Fixtures

[x] Zero Configuration!

[x] easy to use with jenkins / travis-ci


